        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>Lamentations 1</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                        <l xml:id="Lam-001-x001"><ref n="1" target="#Lam-001-fn1" type="noteAnchor"
                                 /><seg type="commented" corresp="#Lam-001-seg001" /><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ובשם אשר לו הגדילה
                                והממלכה׃ אכתוב מגילת איכה׃</foreign>
                            <anchor type="commented" xml:id="Lam-001-seg001" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            <ref n="2" target="#Lam-001-fn2" type="noteAnchor" /><seg
                                type="commented" corresp="#Lam-001-seg002" />
                            <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בלשונ חחמוני כדי
                                לחטעימו לאדוני הבלתי מבינים טעם לשון הקודש׃ וזהו׃הפשט היקר </foreign>
                            <anchor type="commented" xml:id="Lam-001-seg002" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">א׳ ישבה בדד העיר
                                רבתי עם</foreign>
                        </l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                        <l xml:id="Lam-001-x002">Qyna sözleri Jirmijahu ol navinin ki qyna uḥudu
                            verenligi ücün
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                             šaharynyn Jerušalajimnin da barmaɣy ücün Jisraʿelnin galutqa baslady
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                             da ajtty.<ref n="3" target="#Lam-001-fn3" type="noteAnchor" /></l>
                        <l n="1" xml:id="Lam-001-001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">איכה </foreign>
                             Vaj necik necik olturdu jalɣyz ezi ol sahar qajsy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                             edi burundan köp uluslu da boldu tul qatyn kibik qajsy aɣaraqlyq
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                             eteredi ḥanlyqlarda bijcelik eteredi valajatlar arasyna haligine
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                             boldu ol ezi jasaq berivcige.</l>
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Lam-001-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בכו </foreign>
                             Jylama jylajdy kece byla
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                             da jasy anyn jajaɣy istinedi küngiz joḥtu anar jubatuvcu bar süver-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                             lerinden bar dostlary anyn tandylar anar boldular anar dusmanlarɣa.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                        <l n="3" xml:id="Lam-001-003"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">גלתה </foreign>
                             Olcaɣa bardy Juhuda qyjyndan da köpliginden qulluqnun ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                             olturdu ḥanlyqlar arasyna tapmady tynclyq bar quvuvculary anyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                             jettiler any ol qysyq orunlar arasyna.</l>
                        <l n="4" xml:id="Lam-001-004"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">דרכי </foreign>
                             Jollary Cijonnun
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                             jaslydylar kelivcü joɣundan moʿedge bar qabaqlary anyn qajɣylydylar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                             kohenleri tistunadylar boj qyzlary anyn munajɣandylar da ol ezi de
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                             acydy anar.</l>
                        <l n="5" xml:id="Lam-001-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">היו </foreign>
                             Boldular tar berivcileri anyn basqa dusman-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                             lary anyn tync olturadylar ki H qajɣyrtty any köpligi ücün
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                             tanmaqlarynyn jas ulanlary anyn bardylar jesirge alnynda tar beriv-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                             cinin.</l>
                        <l n="6" xml:id="Lam-001-006"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצא </foreign>
                             Da cyqty ʒymatyndan Cijonnun bar hermetli eli
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                             anyn boldular aɣaraqlary anyn olenler kibik ki tapmasalar kitiv
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                             da bardylar kücsiz alnynda kuvuvcunun.</l>
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Lam-001-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">זכרה </foreign>
                             Saɣyndy sahary
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                             Jerušalajimnin qyjynly da acylyq künlerinde özünün bar suqlancy
                            nerselerin
                            <milestone unit="page" n="138v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                             ki ediler avaldaɣy künlerden tiskende ulusu anyn qoluna ta beriv-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                             cinin da joɣedi bolusuvcu anar kördiler any tar berivciler küldiler
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                             verenlik<supplied reason="lost">lerin</supplied>den<ref n="4"
                                target="#Lam-001-fn4" type="noteAnchor" /> anyn.</l>
                        <l n="8" xml:id="Lam-001-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">חטא </foreign>
                             Ullu jazyq jazyqly boldu Jerušalajim anyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                             ücün ḥorluqqa boldu bar syjlavculary anyn burundan haligine ḥorladylar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                             any ki kordiler ajipli islerin anyn daɣy ol ezi de küstunady da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                             qajtady ködergi bar saɣyslaryndan.</l>
                        <l n="9" xml:id="Lam-001-009"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">טמאתה </foreign>
                             Hanuz bolɣanda murdarlyɣy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                             anyn eteklerinde saɣynmady sonɣusun özinin da endi tamasa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                             enmekler joɣedi jubatuvcu anar körgün e H osol qyjynymny ki ulɣajtty
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                             verenlik qylma dusman.</l>
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Lam-001-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ידו </foreign>
                             Qolun sundu tar berivcü dusman bar suqlancy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                             nerseleri istine anyn ki kördü ḥanlyqlarny keldiler miqdašyna anyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                             qajsylary ücün bujurdun ki kelmegejler qahalɣa da sana.</l>
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Lam-001-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כל </foreign>
                             Bar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                             ulusu anyn kistunadylar qoladylar etmek berdiler suqlancy nerselerin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                             jem ücün esewletme ʒanlaryn körgün e H da baqqyn ki boldum
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                             ḥorlanɣan.</l>
                        <l n="12" xml:id="Lam-001-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">לוא </foreign>
                             Ajtylmaɣaj sizge bundij verenlik bar asuvcular
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                             jol byla baɣynynyz da köriniz bardymo syzlav syzlavym kibik menim ki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                             zaval qyldy mana ki qajɣyrtty H qahir acuv kininde.</l>
                        <l n="13" xml:id="Lam-001-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ממרום </foreign>
                             Bijik
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                             kökten ijdi ot süveklerimde da jancty alarny jajdy av ajaq-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                             laryma qajtardy meni kedergi berdi meni qajɣyly har kün syzlavlu.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                        <l n="14" xml:id="Lam-001-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">שקד </foreign>
                             Jirildi bojunsasy tanmaqlarymnyn qudratynda anyn butaqlandylar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                             mindiler bojnum istine sirindirdi kücümni berdi meni H qoluna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                             andij dusmannyn ki bolalmajmen turma.</l>
                        <l n="15" xml:id="Lam-001-015"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">סלה </foreign>
                             Basqalady bar küclile-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                             rimni H ortamda caɣyrdy istime jomulmaq zaman syndyrma igit-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                             lerimni caɣyrbent bastyrdy H boj ʒymatyna Juhudanyn.</l>
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Lam-001-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">על</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="page" n="139r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                             Bular ücün men jilajmen közim menim endiredi suvlarny kibik jasny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                             ki jiraq ketti menden jubatuvcu esevletivcü ʒanymny boldular uvul-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                             larym menim qajɣylylar ki kicejdi dusman.</l>
                        <l n="17" xml:id="Lam-001-017"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">פרשה </foreign>
                             Ez qollary byla syndy-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                             ryp aldy Cijon etmek ezine joɣedi jubatuvcu anar symarlady H Jaʿaqovɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                             civrelerinde tar berivcilerin anyn boldu Jerušalajim igis nersege
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                             aralarynda alarnyn.</l>
                        <l n="18" xml:id="Lam-001-018"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">צדיק </foreign>
                             Rasttyr ol H qacan ki bujruɣuna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                             anyn tandym tynlanyz endi bar ol uluslar da köriniz syzlavymny boj
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                             qyzlarym da jigitlerim bardylar jesirge.</l>
                        <l n="19" xml:id="Lam-001-019"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">קראתי </foreign>
                             Caɣyrdym süverleri-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                             me alar aladttylar meni kohenlerim da qartlarym saharda tyndylar ki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                             izlediler jem ezlerine ki esevlettiler ʒanlaryn. (<foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ראה</foreign>
                             ) <supplied reason="lost">2o</supplied> Körgin e
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                             H ki tardy mana bavursaqlarym qarardylar civirildi jür<supplied
                                reason="lost">e</supplied>gim<ref n="5" target="#Lam-001-fn5"
                                type="noteAnchor" /> icimde ki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                             tanma tandym tysqarydan tuv eter qylyc ickiriden qorquvu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                             elimnin.</l>
                        <l n="21" xml:id="Lam-001-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">שמעו </foreign>
                             Esittiler ki tistunɣan menmen joḥtu jubatuvcu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                             mana bar dusmanlarym esittiler jamanymny da kuvandylar ki sen qyldyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                             jamanny birgeme keltirgin alarɣa da zaval künnü ki caɣyrdyn da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                             bolsunlar menim kibik.</l>
                        <l n="22" xml:id="Lam-001-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">תבא </foreign>
                             Kelsin jamanlyqlary alarnyn alnyna senin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                             da jengillik qylɣyn alarɣa ki necik jengillik qyldyn mana köpligi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                             ücün tanmaqlarymnyn ki köptiler tistunmaqlarym da jüregim boldu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                             syzlavlu.</l>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app>
                        <note xml:id="Lam-001-fn1" type="footnote">Heb. ‘And in the name of the one
                            to whom the greatness and the kingdom belong. I will write the scroll of
                            Eikha (Lamentations)’.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Lam-001-fn2" type="footnote">Heb. ‘In the common language in
                            order to give the taste of the holy language to the lords who does not
                            know how it tastes. And this is this precious translation
                            (interpretation)’.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Lam-001-fn3" type="footnote">An introduction added by the
                            copyist.</note>
